notesStmt.note: Title from title page (f. 3r). Spine title: Leonarducci geometria pratica.

msContents.summary: Problems in geometry applied to military strategy, architecture, navigation; with diagrams, drawings of fortifications and other buildings, tables of logarithms, drawings of solid geometric forms, with an index.

msItem.title: Duplicate table of contents, Loose note 1, Side 1

supportDesc.extent: 244 leaves : 235 x 180 mm. bound to 246 x 190 mm. +
supportDesc.foliation: Paper, i (contemporary paper) + 244 + i (contemporary paper); [1-244]; modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto.

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a cursive script by a single hand.

decoDesc.decoNote: Illustrated with pen-and-ink diagrams throughout, mostly drawn on recto with problems written out on facing verso.

binding.p: Contemporary pasteboard. First quire loose, pages or quire missing between f. 4-5.

keywords.term: Military art and science--Early works to 1800
